            , were indicted for <rs id="t17690906-83-off439" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17690906-83-off439" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17690906-83-off439" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing twenty-three yards of printed linen, value 5 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17690906-83-victim813" type="victimName">
